ously close intervals. this is where we saw the first parts of their amazing maneuverability such as their ability to fly in acute angles at such increased velocity, as one made a sharp v and headed in a different direction. while these two were playing, the third appeared to start giving chase before joining as part of the group. we noticed as they increased speed, their lights would blink faster and faster until they were nothing but a blur, such as a meteor with no tail. when they slowed, their white lights blinked less and turned to three red lights at a slight pause before they resumed flying right, circling to left and dropping to the v at a lower altitude. they did this many times. prior to seeing them, we had noticed numerous airplanes (regular ones). at approximately 2200, it seemed the area became a no-fly zone, until approximately 2235 when an airplane entered from the left, at which time, the unknown aircraft proceeded to flee the area, reappearing at a lower altitude, when the airplane had passed. they resumed their ���������acrobatics��������� for another approximately 15 minutes before leaving. these three aircraft made a loud, deep, growling engine noise��������� deeper than any combat aircraft i have encountered in my 5 years of service as an infantryman. i am unsure about what type of aircrafts these may have been, but i did see similar aircraft, to the first we witnessed, at extreme altitudes 56 miles away at my home in lexington, sc the night before. they appeared as dots in the sky with one brightening then separating, going in different directions, covering distances that would baffle you. i believe in reverse engineering that is kept from the public by the military. it is my belief these aircraft could possibly be proof of such. [witness name deleted\\cms\\tg]"],"Date Submitted":"08/14/2010 11:58 UTC","map":"<A HREF = \"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=33.928885,+-80.338749(25092)&iwloc=A&hl=en\"> mufon case (25092) map </A>","Viewing Distance":"